The scripts and files in this folder are used on the Terminal machine,
which acts as the gateway into the police servers and is located at Timble HQ.

These files should be placed at /Users/terminal/Sites/lokalepolitie.be/ on the terminal machine.

Note:

- Make sure to install rsync 3.0.9 with iconv support. See rsync.sh.

List of files and their purpose:
--------------------------------

- rsync.sh is used to backup the files and mysql dumps from the production server
  (rsync.exclude is a list of files/folders that should not be synced when backing up)
